text: Nancy Alejandra Ortega (born 31 March 1990) is a Mexican volleyball player. == Career == She played at the 2006 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, 2007 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, 2009 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, 2009 Women's NORCECA Volleyball Championship, and 2011 Women's NORCECA Volleyball Championship. She played for Baja California. == References == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican volleyball players Category:People from Baja California (state)
